dialogue: Right? And she's in your boss's office right now.
Uh huh. Sure. That woman is in this building. That's not just a random picture you grabbed from the internet to convince me you're meant to be here.
Well, two can play at that game. I loooooove pie.
You don't like pie? Who doesn't like pie?
What? No, I love pie. I just said.
Dude, do you not know how sarcasm works?
Ah, crap. My secret is out.
